Description: Get ready to be impressed! This rare Art Deco gem on the South Hill and close to Perry District! The home boasts 4 beds/3 baths and many updates. With a completely brand new roof, updated deck (cover, railing and stairs), new electric hot water heater, and new electrical furnace and A/C with electronic air cleaner and Reme-Halo purifier. The air of this home is cleansed of viruses, bacteria, and allergens! Also with the home design and updates to switch to all electric, the home is highly efficient and environmentally friendly. The main floor has a spectacular living room with fireplace and refinished white oak wood flooring. Head out the to the back yard to enjoy the covered patio and fire pit. The guest room has been updated with soft-close California closet system creating the perfect zen space. The icing on the cake is the deck just off the upstairs bedroom. This deck is all new with a walk on roof system, glass railing, stairs to the backyard, and privacy screen. Come enjoy the peaceful tranquility!

Better than new, this chic, remodeled home with eagle eye views of the Sound and the Kingston ferry is the one you've been waiting for! Boasting an open floor plan on the main level with chef inspired kitchen featuring custom, soft close cabinets, quartz counters, and ss appliances. Flowing engineered hardwoods set the stage for the captivating views of the Sound and mountains from the sun-drenched deck, spacious living room flooded with natural light, and the retreat like primary en-suite with private deck which provides a quiet, peaceful option to enjoy the spectacular view. The flexible floor-plan allows for configuration to suit any need while providing quick and easy access to the Kingston/Edmonds ferry and Seattle fast ferry. Hurry!!

As you enter the tree-lined entrance of Park Ridge Estates you will notice the community park & sports court. This gorgeous remodeled home features vaulted ceilings, newer hardwood floors, a modern kitchen with quartz countertops, soft close cabinets, stainless steel appliances, & several USB ports built in. There is a 4th bedroom on the main level adjacent to a newly remodeled bathroom. Enjoy the spacious cedar deck with a paver patio off the kitchen surrounded by the newly fenced backyard. The luxurious primary bedroom includes an extra room with a fireplace that could be made into a spacious at-home office, nursery, or work-out space. Don't miss the 3-car garage, storage abounds! Fantastic location with easy access to both I-5 and 405.

Skyline View Home and Property features Expansive City Views from the top of Skyline Drive. Rare 4.5+ acres close into town. Minutes to hospital, racquet club and multi-seasonal recreation. Home features updated kitchen with quartz countertops, cherry soft close cabinetry and drawers, stainless appliances, double ovens, breakfast nook, butler bar and wine fridge. New quartz counters in bathrooms, new Trex deck, stunning inground pool, greenhouse and private treed landscaping with top of the world views. They aren't making anymore land....especially with Wenatchee Skyline Views! Adjacent 8.5+ acres for sale as well.
